  <brief_title>Trial of Levofloxacin as Prophylaxis After Allogeneic Stem Cell Transplantation (SCT)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Multicenter Trial With Levofloxacin as Prophylaxis for Bacterial Infections in Immunocompromised Patients After Allogeneic Transplantation of Hematopoietic Stem Cells</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
