  <source>Charite University, Berlin, Germany</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy of levofloxacin to prevent bacterial
      infections in the postneutropenic period in patients who have undergone allogeneic stem cell
      transplantation (SCT).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
